SIMPLE: optimist
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Optimist
<hw>Op"ti*mist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>optimiste</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Metaph.)</fld> <def>One who holds the opinion that
all events are ordered for the best.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who looks on the bright side of things, or takes
hopeful views; one who experiences optimism{2}; -- opposed to
<ant>pessimist</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Optimistic</ent>⟦br⟧
